  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Radishes are fast and cool-season friendly.</li>
    <li>Direct sow early and again for fall using first frost as the anchor.</li>
    <li>Quality is mostly temperature-driven.</li>
    <li>Hard freezes at 32°F (0°C) end unprotected growth.</li>
  </ol>
</section>
